---
---

<header class="hero">
  <div class="wrap hero-grid">
    <div>
      <span class="hero-kicker"><span class="pulse"></span>Deja de adivinar. Empieza a saber.</span>
      <h1>La <em>radiografía</em> de tus grupos de WhatsApp.</h1>
      <p class="lead hero-sub">Quién escribe e interactúa, quién va a las actividades, quién aporta su granito de arena... y quién solo está por estar.</p>
      <p class="hero-product">App Android que analiza tus chats exportados de WhatsApp con IA, <strong>directamente en tu teléfono</strong>. Arrastra un <code>.zip</code> y en 30 segundos tienes todo.</p>

      <div class="hero-ctas">
        <a class="store-btn" href="#descargar">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M3.609 1.814L13.792 12 3.61 22.186a.996.996 0 0 1-.61-.92V2.734a1 1 0 0 1 .609-.92zm10.89 10.893l2.302 2.302-10.937 6.333 8.635-8.635zm3.199-3.199l2.807 1.626a1 1 0 0 1 0 1.732l-2.808 1.626L15.207 12l2.491-2.492zM5.864 2.658L16.802 8.99l-2.303 2.303-8.635-8.635z"/></svg>
          <span><span class="sub">Disponible en</span><span class="name">Google Play</span></span>
        </a>
        <button class="store-btn store-btn-ios" id="iosTrigger" type="button" aria-haspopup="dialog">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M17.05 20.28c-.98.95-2.05.8-3.08.35-1.09-.46-2.09-.48-3.24 0-1.44.62-2.2.44-3.06-.35C2.79 15.25 3.51 7.59 9.05 7.31c1.35.07 2.29.74 3.08.8 1.18-.24 2.31-.93 3.57-.84 1.51.12 2.65.72 3.4 1.8-3.12 1.87-2.38 5.98.48 7.13-.57 1.5-1.31 2.99-2.53 4.08zM12.03 7.25c-.15-2.23 1.66-4.07 3.74-4.25.29 2.58-2.34 4.5-3.74 4.25z"/></svg>
          <span><span class="sub">Avísame en</span><span class="name">App Store</span></span>
        </button>
      </div>
      <p class="hero-fineprint">Gratis para empezar · Sin registro · Sin tarjeta · Tus datos nunca salen de tu teléfono</p>

      <div class="trust-chips">
        <span class="trust-chip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="11" rx="2"/><path d="M7 11V7a5 5 0 0110 0v4"/></svg>100% local</span>
        <span class="trust-chip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M4.93 4.93l14.14 14.14"/></svg>Sin registro</span>
        <span class="trust-chip"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 11-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>Tus datos nunca salen de tu teléfono</span>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- HERO GIF -->
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-gif-card">
        <div class="hero-gif-label">
          <span>Loop · 6s</span>
          <span class="dots"><span class="dot on"></span><span class="dot"></span><span class="dot"></span></span>
        </div>
        <div class="gif gif-hero">
          <div class="phone-frame">
            <div class="phone-screen">
              <div class="screen-header"><span>15:25</span><span class="r">●●●</span></div>

              <div class="scene scene-1">
                <div class="zip">
                  <div class="zip-icon">ZIP</div>
                  <div class="zip-name">chat.zip</div>
                </div>
              </div>

              <div class="scene scene-2">
                <div class="spin"></div>
                <div class="proc-txt">Analizando <strong>4,287</strong> mensajes</div>
                <div class="proc-bar"><div class="proc-fill"></div></div>
                <div class="proc-txt" style="margin-top:10px;opacity:.5">IA on-device · Sin subir nada</div>
              </div>

              <div class="scene scene-3">
                <div class="score-ring">
                  <svg viewBox="0 0 80 80">
                    <circle class="track" cx="40" cy="40" r="35"/>
                    <circle class="prog" cx="40" cy="40" r="35"/>
                  </svg>
                  <div class="score-num">87</div>
                </div>
                <div style="text-align:center;font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:9px;color:var(--ink-3);letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:12px">Salud del grupo</div>
                <div class="metrics">
                  <div class="metric"><div class="n">45</div><div class="l">Activos</div></div>
                  <div class="metric warn"><div class="n">8</div><div class="l">Riesgo</div></div>
                  <div class="metric danger"><div class="n">3</div><div class="l">Inactivos</div></div>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="gif-progress"></div>
      </div>

      <div class="hero-float-card hero-float-1">
        <div style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--ink-3);text-transform:uppercase">Alerta</div>
        <div style="font-weight:500;margin-top:4px"><em style="color:var(--brand-2);font-family:var(--f-display)">3 miembros</em> no asistieron a los últimos 2 eventos</div>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-float-card hero-float-2">
        <div style="font-family:var(--f-mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:.08em;color:var(--ink-3);text-transform:uppercase">Pico de actividad</div>
        <div style="font-weight:500;margin-top:4px">Domingos 18:00 <span style="color:var(--accent)">🔥</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>
